            "title": "港股午後升122點   百度升逾6%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股午後轉升，現報26058，升122點或0.47%，為暫時高位。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科指升40點或0.72%，報5656點; 國指升70點或0.77%，報9177點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230712-124434_source-web_09888-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：百度官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/bplib_20230712-124434_source-web_09888-1_source-web_-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：百度官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交1342.33億元。 </p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">百度(09888)升6.05%報122.8元，為表現最佳藍籌股，傳分拆AI晶片崑崙芯在港上市。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內險股升幅擴大，中國平安(02318)升5.91%，報60元，貢獻恒指34點 ; 中國人壽(02628)升4.93%，報28.1元，兩者成交俱入20大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">江銅(00358)升5.47%，報35.88元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小米(01810)升2.33%，報42.98元。</p>\n</div>",
